---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="text-center section-padding bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-skycare-light rounded-3xl shadow-sm">
  <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-skycare-darkblue mb-4">
    깨끗함과 따뜻함을 한 번에.
  </h2>
  <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg mb-10">
    가족처럼 정성껏, <strong>스카이케어존</strong>이 책임집니다.
  </p>
  <a href="#contact" class="btn-skycare w-full sm:w-auto text-base sm:text-lg px-8 py-4">무료 견적 문의</a>
</section>

<section id="services" class="mt-20 sm:mt-24">
  <h3 class="text-center section-title mb-10">우리의 주요 서비스</h3>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all p-8 text-center">
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg md:text-xl text-skycare-darkblue mb-2">
          에어컨 청소
        </h4>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
          냉방 효율 향상, 곰팡이 제거로 쾌적한 실내공기 유지
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all p-8 text-center">
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg md:text-xl text-skycare-darkblue mb-2">
          클리닝 서비스
        </h4>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
          사무실, 매장, 시설 맞춤 청소로 최상의 위생 환경 조성
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all p-8 text-center">
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg md:text-xl text-skycare-darkblue mb-2">
          방역 서비스
        </h4>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
          인체에 안전한 약품으로 해충 완전 차단
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section id="contact" class="mt-28 text-center py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-skycare-light to-white rounded-3xl shadow-sm">
    <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-skycare-darkblue mb-4">
      지금 바로 문의하세요
    </h3>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 text-sm md:text-base">
      빠른 견적과 친절한 상담을 약속드립니다.
    </p>
    <a href="tel:010-3201-0019" class="btn-skycare px-8 py-4 text-base md:text-lg">
      전화 문의하기
    </a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
